data.description: This stunning 5-bedroom, 3.5-bath home, designed in a timeless traditional split layout. Complete with three car-garage, it provides ample parking and storage space. This home is situated on over half an acre, perfect for all your outdoor activities. The formal dining area adds an elegant touch while the open concept design creates a seamless flow between living spaces. Perfect for modern living. Equipped with electric fireplace for an elegant touch. Indulge in luxury within the master suite, a sanctuary of comfort and style spacious walk-in closet, offers storage for your wardrobe, keeping everything organized. The master bathroom, boasts a standalone tub, inviting you to unwind and tranquility, the elegant glass shower with double shower heads as a modern touch, creating a spa like experience right at home. As well as four other oversized bedrooms, enjoy the same attention to detail. Situated in close proximity to Belton Lake. Huge Buyer incentives are available.  Seller will pay up to  $20,000 towards buyer closing costs/Rate Buy Down.
